events.name: August Drone Fun - Intro to FPV and Proximity Flying
events.description: Nice easy location, walking distance from Commonwealth MRT. If you get lost or can't find us, call/sms/whatsapp me - 91001743. Come along and practice your FPV flying through and around trees and obstacles, get an introduction to the equipment and skills you will need, get help with getting your equipment running, or just hang out and watch others flying. Singapore Drone Fun Meetup is a non-commercial activity and while we promote and encourage safe and legal flying, all participants join at their own risk and liability.
events.location: Margaret Drive Park by Queensway, Margaret Close, Singapore
